<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.1">
<l>nīṇākam cuṟṟi neṭuvarainaṭ ṭāḻkaṭalaip</l>
<l>pēṇāṉ kaṭaintamutam koṇṭukanta pemmāṉai</l>
<l>pūṇāra mārvaṉaip puḷḷūrum poṉmalaiyai</l>
<l>kāṇātār kaṇṇeṉṟuṅ kaṇṇalla kaṇṭāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The eyes of those who do not see the golden mountain that rides a bird,</l>
<l>The one with a jewel-covered chest, the great lord who was pleased,</l>
<l>Having gotten ambrosia churning the deep sea with care,</l>
<l>Having fixed a high mountain [and] wound a long serpent,</l>
<l rend="indent">are never eyes; [this] we have seen.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
